% Swift Language Ontology - CNL Format
% Extends oo_ontology.cnl with Swift-specific concepts

% File/Module types
Every swift-compilation-unit is a compilation-unit.
Every swift-module is a module.

% Type definitions
Every swift-class is a class.
Every swift-struct is a struct.
Every swift-enum is an enum.
Every swift-protocol is an interface.
Every swift-extension is a class.
Every swift-type-alias is a type-alias.

% Members
Every swift-method is a method.
Every swift-function is a function.
Every swift-field is a field.
Every swift-property is a property.
Every swift-constructor is a constructor.
Every swift-enum-member is an enum-member.
Every swift-subscript is a property.

% Parameters
Every swift-parameter is a parameter.

% Import
Every swift-import is an import.

% Exception handling
Every swift-try-block is a try-block.
Every swift-catch-clause is a catch-clause.
Every swift-throw-statement is a throw-statement.

% Control flow
Every swift-return-statement is a return-statement.

% Other
Every swift-variable is a variable.
Every swift-constant is a field.
Every swift-reference is a reference.
Every swift-attribute is an attribute.
Every swift-anonymous-function is an anonymous-function.

% Swift-Specific Concepts
Every final-class is a class.
Every open-class is a class.
Every convenience-initializer is a constructor.
Every required-initializer is a constructor.
Every deinitializer is a method.

% Access Modifiers
Every public-member is a member.
Every private-member is a member.
Every internal-member is a member.
Every fileprivate-member is a member.
Every open-member is a member.

% Code Smells
Every swift-god-class is a god-class.
Every swift-long-method is a long-method.
